requirement_analysis.user:
Please analyze the following agent requirements and provide a structured JSON specification. The JSON should include: purpose, capabilities (as an array), and knowledge_domains (as an array). Each capability should have name, description, and dependencies fields. Example JSON format:
```json
{
  "purpose": "string",
  "capabilities": [
    {
      "name": "string",
      "description": "string",
      "dependencies": ["string"]
    }
  ],
  "knowledge_domains": ["string"]
}
```

Requirements: {requirements}

capability_design.user:
Design a detailed specification for the "{capability_name}" capability described as: {capability_description}. The response must be a JSON object with the following structure:
```json
{
  "name": "string",
  "description": "string",
  "parameters": {
    "param1": "value1"
  },
  "implementation_notes": "string",
  "dependencies": ["string"],
  "performance_metrics": ["string"]
}
```
